      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping must demonstrate that simulation input parameters (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties) match experimental conditions within defined tolerances.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping document was produced. Geometric fidelity of the CAD model relative to the physical test article was assumed but not verified with metrology data."
