    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for submission despite multiple credibility factor gaps. Six of thirteen factors remain not-assessed at MRL 5, and all seven assessed factors fall below required levels. The package is accepted as a complete documentation artefact recording the current state of evidence; it does not constitute regulatory acceptance of the model for clinical decision-making. Remediation actions are required before model use.",
